MWEB has launched a promotion on its data-only packages, offering new subscribers 2 months of free access. This promotion is only available on 22 or 23 February, and is only applicable to the company’s capped and uncapped data-only ADSL products. MWEB highlighted that there are no long-term contracts associated with this deal, and that no credit checks apply. MWEB’s month-to-month capped products start at R145 for 150GB, which include uncapped night-time data. The company’s month-to-month uncapped pricing starts at R79 for a 2Mbps service. MWEB highlighted that the free period applies for 60 days from date of sign up, and that cancellations are subject to a calendar month’s notice.